      "content": "But healing... that is such a heavy, impossible word. You speak of rising above, yet I find I have no strength left to even stand. To \"rise\" implies there is a peak to reach, but I see only a descent. Is there not a certain, quiet dignity in simply accepting that some fires are meant to burn out? To stop fighting the tide and let the dark water pull me under, peacefully?",
